### GET - Obtener vino por ID (cambiar el ID)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/vinos/ID_VINO
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### GET - Obtener vino por ID (admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/vinos/ID_VINO
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### PUT - Actualizar vino (cambiar el ID)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/vinos/ID_VINO
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "nombre": "Vino Tinto Premium",
  "precio": 18.00,
  "graduacion": 14.0,
  "tipo": "Tinto Crianza",
  "descripcion": "Tinto premium de cuerpo medio"
}

### DELETE - Eliminar vino (cambiar el ID)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/vinos/ID_VINO
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

