### ================================
### PETICIONES DE COMANDES
### ================================

### POST - Crear comanda amb usuari autenticat -> 201
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/comandes
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

{
  "items": [
    {
      "tipus": "cerveza",
      "producteId": "{{cervezaId}}",
      "quantitat": 2
    },
    {
      "tipus": "vino",
      "producteId": "{{vinoId}}",
      "quantitat": 1
    }
  ]
}

### POST - Crear comanda sense token -> 401
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/comandes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "items": [
    {
      "tipus": "cerveza",
      "producteId": "{{cervezaId}}",
      "quantitat": 1
    }
  ]
}

### POST - Crear comanda amb dades incorrectes -> 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/comandes
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

{
  "items": [
    {
      "tipus": "cerveza",
      "producteId": "",
      "quantitat": 0
    }
  ]
}

### GET - Consultar les meves comandes -> 200
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/comandes/me
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### PATCH - Subir imagen de vino (admin)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/vinos/{{vinoId}}/imatge
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----AstroBoundary

------AstroBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="imatge"; filename="vino-prova.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./uploads-proves/vino-prova.jpg
------AstroBoundary--
